MAS_UTrack_V003 A Plethora Of Twinkies Abound! By: Killer Fish (Todd Showalter) of Late Nite Software Labs -------------------------------- Written on or about Feb/94 (c) Written on UltraTracker v1.5, this happy little ditty is a celebration of all which is not calculus mid-terms. Enjoy it in the light, fluffy, unassuming way that it was intended.
Greetz to my list of tracked music heroes (alpha. order): Captain/Image Beyond Music C.C.Catch Dreamy Nights Remix Ryan Cramer The Power Of Wind Deathjester Lektrophile Dr. Awesome Bridge Lizardking Lizardking's Theme Nuke Acid Jazz pt 1 & 2 Purple Motion Starshine PM Romeo Knight Boesendorfer
PSS I can be contacted by snail- mail (no e-mail yet) at: Todd Showalter 24 Broomfield Crt. Brampton, Ontario, Canada. L6Z-1T5.
If you like my music and need something tracked, drop me a line. I'll probably be free. Gotta speed, keid...
Killer Fish
